-monitor-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewithout%20a%20safety%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20its%20service%20in%20the%20Texan%20city%20is%20still%20small%2C%20with%20around%2050%20active%20vehicles%2C%20according%20to%20a%20community%20tracker%20run%20by%20Austin-based%20robotaxi%20watcher%20Ethan%20McKenna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Tesla%20would%20have%20robotaxis%20operating%20in%20%26quot%3Bsomewhere%20between%20a%20quarter%20and%20half%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20US%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20pending%20regulatory%20approval%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20production%20on%20its%20dedicated%20Cybercab%20robotaxi%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20stops%20at%20a%20stop%20sign.%20A%20Waymo%20follows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69613f90832e0ef1ead77f58%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221946%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20launched%20its%20self-driving%20tax%20service%20in%202025.%20This%20year%2C%20its%20facing%20several%20scaling%20deadlines.%3Cp%3EJay%20Janner%2FAustin%20American-Statesman%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20added%20that%20Tesla's%20focus%20this%20year%20would%20be%20on%20building%20out%20its%20robotaxi%20service%2C%20noting%20he%20didn't%20expect%20the%20company%20to%20begin%20collecting%20%26quot%3Bmeaningful%20revenue%26quot%3B%20from%20autonomous%20ride-hailing%20until%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20that%20they%20get%20into%20what%20I%20believe%20will%20probably%20be%20roughly%20about%2030%20cities%20this%20year.%202026%20is%20the%20build-out%20of%20robotaxis%2C%202027%20is%20where%20you'll%20start%20to%20see%20more%20monetization%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Tesla's%20robotaxi%20service%20reaches%20escape%20velocity%2C%20Narayan%20said%20he%20expects%20it%20to%20transfo