uot%3B%20Gerry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20a%20half-dozen%20local%20business%20owners%2C%20including%20Gerry%2C%20about%20their%20decision%20to%20take%20a%20stance%20on%20immigration%20agents'%20presence%20in%20Portland%2C%20including%20whether%20to%20post%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20the%20table%3A%20Should%20they%20go%20along%20with%20calls%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-strike-ice-protest-minneapolis-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshutting%20businesses%20and%20schools%20on%20Friday%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20what%20organizers%20hope%20will%20be%20a%20nationwide%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerry%20said%20that%20some%20owners%20he's%20been%20speaking%20with%20favor%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20stoppage%2C%20and%20others%20are%20calling%20for%20businesses%20to%20remain%20open%20to%20divert%20profits%20to%20groups%20helping%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%20this%20week%2C%20Gerry%20said%2C%20he's%20flip-flopped%20over%20whether%20to%20keep%20the%20restaurant%20open%20on%20Friday.%20His%20current%20thought%3A%20Close%20for%20the%20day%20and%20donate%20weekend%20proceeds%20to%20charities%20helping%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20immigration%20sweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20sorts%20of%20calculations%20that%20many%20small-business%20owners%20across%20the%20US%20have%20considered%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20The%20question%20has%20felt%20especially%20urgent%20lately%20in%20Portland%2C%20a%20seaside%20city%20of%20about%2070%2C000%2C%20where%20immigration%20officials%20have%20had%20a%20more%20visible%20presence%20over%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20of%20corporate%20America's%20top%20executives%20have%20weighed%20in%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminneapolis-ice-shootings-ceos-response-trump-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estatements%20about%20the%20immigration%20actions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20small-business%20owners%20%E2%80%94%20answering%20phones%20and%20facing%20customers%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20are%20making%20personal%20choices%20about%20whether%20to%20publicly%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20workers%20and%20owners%20at%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20businesses%20Business%20Insider%20visited%20didn't%20want%20to%20discuss%20the%20immigration%20issue%20because%20they%20said%20it%20didn't%20pertain%20to%20their%20day-to-day%20operations.%20Others%20said%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20upset%20neighboring%20businesses%20or%20draw%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214fe048b-745e-400c-a3af-40d8b1e06104%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'white%20lady%20who%20can%20yell'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGerry%20said%20he%20saw%20putting%20up%20the%20sign%2C%20created%20by%20a%20Portland%20artist%2C%20as%20a%20way%20to%20amplify%20his%20staffers'%20voices%20and%20support%20anyone%20who%20might%20be%20fearful%20of%20getting%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20immigration%20sweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20contacted%20restaurant%20review%20sites%20to%20flag%20the%20negative%20ratings%2C%20and%20he%20and%20his%20co-owners%20instructed%20the%20restaurant's%20more%20than%2050%20staffers%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20negative%20phone%20calls.%20He%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Escreenshots%20of%20commenters%20encouraging%20people%20to%20%26quot%3Breview%20bomb%26quot%3B%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Eden%20Millecchia%20hung%20a%20%26quot%3BNo%20ICE%26quot%3B%20poster%20in%20the%20window%20of%20her%20airy%20shop%2C%20called%20Flowers%20%26amp%3B%20Candy.%20The%20following%20week%2C%20she%20attended%20an%20online%20training%20conducted%20by%20a%20chapter%20of%20the%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20about%20where%20federal%20agents%20are%20permitted%20to%20go%20within%20a%20business%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20warrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillecchia%20said%20she%20feels%20she's%20in%20a%20more%20privileged%20position%20to%20speak%20up%20than%20some%20other%20shopkeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20white%20lady%20who%20can%20yell%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20Millecchia%20said%2C%20motioning%20toward%20the%20poster%2C%20the%20sign%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhollow%20gesture%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20other%20than%20the%20show%20of%20support%20it%20sends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20tangible%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20the%20drop%20in%20sales%20she's%20seen%20since%20word%20spread%20that%20immigration%20agents%20were%20focusing%20on%20Maine.%20For%20the%20long%20weekend%20that%20included%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Day%20%E2%80%94%20which%20also%20included%20some%20unforgiving%20winter%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20her%20sales%20were%20down%2091%25%20year-over-year%2C%20Millecchia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20killed%20my%20three-day%20weekend%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20keep%20people%20from%20coming%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20federal%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20mean%20fewer%20people%20will%20pick%20up%20the%20CBD%20products%20whose%20sales%20she%20relies%20on%20to%20help%20make%20rent.%20Another%20disruption%3A%20She%20plans%20to%20close%20on%20Friday%20to%20support%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ICE%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20doesn't%20comment%20on%20immigration%20enforcement%20operations.%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22552efb22-2def-415f-b228-add16d1ee557%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20some%20businesses%20are%20responding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20steps%20outside%20Arcana%20Maine%2C%20a%20shop%20that%20sits%20opposite%20a%20small%20park%20and%20sells%20jewelry%20and%20works%20by%20area%20artists%2C%20a%20circular%20table%20recently%20displayed%20free%20business-card-sized%20guides%20to%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20cards%20were%20printed%20in%20English%2C%20Spanish%2C%20French%2C%20Arabic%2C%20Somali%2C%20and%20Kinyarwanda%2C%20which%20is%20spoken%20in%20parts%20of%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20named%20Nico%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20give%20his%20last%20name%2C%20said%20that%20giving%20the%20cards%20a%20prominent%20spot%20was%20a%20way%20to%20help%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20estimated%20that%20foot%20traffic%20at%20the%20store%20had%20fallen%20by%20at%20least%20half%20from%20what's%20typical%20for%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20skate%20shop%20called%20Mocean%2C%20owner%20Jasper%20Tripp%20said%20he%20hung%20a%20%26quot%3BNo%20ICE%26quot%3B%20sign%20because%20it%20aligned%20with%20his%20beliefs.%20Ordinarily%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20tries%20to%20separate%20his%20political%20views%20from%20the%20store%20he%20has%20run%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20feels%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Tripp%20said%20of%20the%20decision%20to%20put%20up%20the%20poster.%20He%20worked%20with%20an%20artist%20to%20design%20an%20anti-ICE%20T-shirt.%20Proceeds%20from%20its%20sale%20will%20go%20to%20charities%20supporting%20immigrants'%20legal%20expenses%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269939b5b-b586-45e7-b9dd-8e3b47a1487d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20'economic%20responsibility'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20business%20owners%2C%20concerns%20go%20beyond%20the%20risk%20of%20alienating%20customers.%20One%20restaurant%20owner%20said%20she%20plans%20to%20shut%20down%20for%20at%20least%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20and%20pay%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20while%20she's%20out%20of%20town.%20Ordinarily%2C%20she%20said%2C%20her%20employees%20would%20run%20the%20restaurant%2C%20which%20has%20an%20entirely%20Spanish-speaking%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20asked%20that%20Business%20Insider%20not%20use%20her%20name%20or%20that%20of%20her%20restaurant%20to%20protect%20her%20employe