y%20hack%20from%20Intercom%20cofounder%20Des%20Traynor.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Broadway%2FSportsfile%20for%20Web%20Summit%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20Superhuman%20calculates%20an%20%26quot%3Balignment%20score%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20how%20well%20his%20time%20matches%20his%20priorities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShishir%20Mehrotra%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20spend%2050%25%20of%20his%20time%20each%20week%20on%20things%20that%20were%20on%20his%20to-do%20list.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMehrotra%20also%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero%20inboxer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShishir%20Mehrotra%20runs%20a%20company%20that's%20all%20about%20productivity%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he's%20got%20a%20meticulous%20method%20to%20track%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuperhuman%20is%20a%20suite%20of%20four%20AI%20productivity%20tools%2C%20including%20Grammarly%2C%20which%20recently%20rebranded%20its%20corporate%20entity%20to%20Superhuman.%20In%20addition%20to%20overseeing%20that%20rebrand%2C%20Mehrotra%20is%20also%20juggling%20board%20seats%20at%20companies%20like%20Walmart%20and%20Spotify%2C%20writing%20a%20coming%20book%20on%20company%20rituals%2C%20and%20raising%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrivago-ceo-productivity-morning-meetings-schedule-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHe%20holds%20himself%20accountable%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20own%20time%20management%20by%20keeping%20track%20of%20how%20well%20he%20completes%20certain%20tasks%2C%20like%20checking%20things%20off%20his%20to-do%20list%20and%20keeping%20his%20inbox%20at%20zero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20Mehrotra%20uses%20a%20productivity%20hack%20from%20Intercom%20cofounder%20Des%20Traynor%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20was%20also%20an%20investor%20in%20Coda%20and%20Superhuman%20Mail%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20now%20products%20within%20Superhuman.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Traynor%20outlined%20his%20framework%20in%20a%20viral%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdestraynor%2Fstatus%2F1143853719135621121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20arguing%20that%20emails%20reflect%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20others%20think%20you%20should%20work%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20to-do%20lists%20show%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20you%20think%20you%20should%20work%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20calendars%20reveal%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20you%20actually%20work%20on.%26quot%3B%20The%20post%2C%20which%20included%20a%20Venn%20diagram%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20three%20buckets%20are%20often%20misaligned%2C%20and%20people%20end%20up%20spending%20most%20of%20their%20time%20on%20what%20others%20think%20is%20important%20rather%20than%20their%20own%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMehrotra%20said%20he%20uses%20Traynor's%20four-step%20time%20management%20guide%20to%20keep%20focused%20on%20what's%20most%20important.%20It%20starts%20with%20clearing%20your%20inbox%2C%20followed%20by%20reorganizing%20your%20calendar%20so%20every%20task%20has%20a%20dedicated%20time%20block.%20The%20third%20step%20is%20sticking%20to%20that%20schedule%2C%20and%20the%20final%20step%20is%20reflecting%20on%20the%20time%20you%20spent%20on%20top%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20evaluating%20for%20adjustments%20in%20the%20next%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMehrotra%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20been%20using%20the%20four-step%20framework%20%26quot%3Breligiously%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20last%20four%20or%20five%20years%2C%20and%20on%20a%20good%20week%2C%20it%20over%20doubles%20the%20amount%20he's%20able%20to%20spend%20on%20his%20to-do%20list%20tasks%20compared%20to%20when%20he%20doesn't%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiving%20yourself%20a%20weekly%20success%20score%20doesn't%20work%20for%20everyone%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20an%20insane%20productivity%20hack%20for%20me%20because%20it%20gives%20visibility%20into%20my%20work%20AND%20gives%20me%20something%20to%20improve%20upon%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehrotra%20wrote%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20about%20the%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225fea975e-4b2e-4864-9563-352f51c09359%5C%22%3EAiming%20for%2050%25%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMehrotra%20said%20he%20reviews%20his%20priorities%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eevery%20Monday%20morning%20and%20sets%20his%20calendar%20with%20his%20executive%20assistant%20and%20chief%20of%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20reviews%20his%20week%2C%20Mehrotra%20calculates%20an%20%26quot%3Balignment%20score%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20the%20overlap%20between%20his%20email%2C%20calendar%2C%20and%20to-do%20list.%20He%20uses%20that%20to%20track%20what%20percentage%20of%20his%20time%20is%20spent%20on%20his%20to-do%20list.%20He%20said%20he%20considers%20a%20score%20of%20around%2050%25%2C%20meaning%20he%20was%20able%20to%20spend%20about%20half%20his%20time%20on%20his%20to-do%20list%2C%20to%20be%20on%20the%20high%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20spend%2050%25%20of%20my%20time%20on%20things%20that%20were%20on%20my%20to-do%20list%2C%20then%20that's%20a%20pretty%20good%20week%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehrotra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7341982563734888449%3Fcollapsed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22655%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMehrotra%20said%20that%20aiming%20for%20100%25%20is%20%26quot%3Bimpractical%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bimpossible.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20without%20using%20Traynor's%20framework%2C%20it%20would%20be%20closer%20to%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20way%20too%20much%20of%20my%20job%20that%20wouldn't%20have%20made%20my%20to%3Cstrong%3E-%3C%2Fstrong%3Edo%20list%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20week%2C%20but%20i