ere's%20a%20lot%20of%20upside%3A%20I've%20reported%20on%20side%20hustlers%20pulling%20in%20impressive%20numbers%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-side-hustle-six-figures-lawyer-fashionably-legal-entrepreneurship-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20full-time%20lawyer%20who%20earns%20%24120%2C000%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20reselling%20sneakers%20and%20apparel%20on%20eBay%20and%20a%20millennial%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-profitable-items-full-time-thrifter-reseller-ebay-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20her%20thrifting%20hobby%20into%20a%20full-time%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20keep%20a%20relatively%20minimal%20closet%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20handful%20of%20items%20I%20no%20longer%20wear.%20Instead%20of%20donating%20or%20tossing%20them%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20reselling.%20How%20hard%20could%20it%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20stopped%20almost%20as%20quickly%20as%20I%20started.%20Here's%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20downloaded%20two%20popular%20clothing%20resale%20apps%3A%20Poshmark%20and%20Mercari.%20Of%20the%20two%2C%20I%20found%20Poshmark%20a%20bit%20easier%20to%20use%2C%20largely%20because%20of%20its%20AI%20assistant%2C%20which%20essentially%20builds%20a%20listing%20for%20you%2C%20including%20descriptions%2C%20titles%2C%20and%20tags%2C%20after%20you%20upload%20photos%20of%20your%20item.%20As%20someone%20who%20doesn't%20know%20clothes%20all%20that%20well%2C%20this%20was%20particularly%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20four%20to%20five%20photos%20per%20item%20against%20a%20clean%2C%20white%20background%20(a%20tip%20from%20top%20resellers)%20and%20priced%20them%20by%20loosely%20comparing%20similar%20listings.%20I%20didn't%20put%20too%20much%20time%20or%20thought%20into%20my%20prices%2C%20figuring%20I%20could%20always%20refine%20them%20later%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%2C%20I%20was%20up%20and%20running%20in%20about%2030%20minutes%20and%20spent%20exactly%20%240.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20my%20Poshmark%20profile%20looks%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elkins%20poshmark%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697a1706e1ba468a96aad71b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Poshmark%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20sale%20came%20through%20Mercari%3A%20a%20striped%20Madewell%20sweater%20I%20listed%20for%20%2420.%20I%20was%20thrilled%20when%20I%20got%20the%20notification%20%E2%80%94%20until%20I%20did%20the%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20%248%20shipping%20fee%20and%20a%20%242%20selling%20fee%2C%20Mercari%20told%20me%20that%20I'd%20made%20%2410.03.%20My%20profit%20got%20knocked%20down%20to%20a%20measly%20six%20bucks%20after%20I%20purchased%20a%20%244%20mailer%20to%20ship%20the%20sweater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elkins%20mercari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697a1753d3c7faef0ecd0f67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Mercari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20slightly%20frustrated%20(was%20a%20couple%20of%20bucks%20really%20worth%20the%20hassle%20of%20printing%20labels%20and%20dropping%20off%20mailers%3F)%2C%20but%20not%20ready%20to%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20next%20two%20sales%20came%20through%20Poshmark%20while%20I%20was%20out%20of%20town%2C%20which%20added%20another%20layer%20of%20inconvenience.%20I%20messaged%20the%20buyers%20to%20let%20them%20know%20I%20would%20ship%20their%20orders%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20returned%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saved%20on%20shipping%20materials%20this%20time%2C%20opting%20to%20use%20mailers%20I%20already%20had%20on%20hand.%20It's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%2C%20because%20of%20my%20pickleball%20business%2C%20I%20already%20had%20a%20label%20printer.%20Without%20that%2C%20I%20may%20not%20have%20embarked%20on%20this%20project%20at%20all.%20Figuring%20out%20how%20to%20print%20shipping%20labels%20at%20a%20FedEx%20%26quot%3BPrint%20%26amp%3B%20Go%26quot%3B%20likely%20would%20have%20sent%20me%20over%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20my%20own%20supplies%2C%20I%20netted%20%2428%20from%20a%20gently%20used%20Tracksmith%20crewneck%20and%20%2438.40%20from%20a%20new%20top%20with%20the%20tags%20still%20on.%20I%20removed%20the%20buyers'%20names%20for%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elkins%20poshmark%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697a17d4a645d11881881fb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Poshmark%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20roughly%20two%20months%2C%20I%20made%20a%20little%20more%20than%20%24100%20across%20five%20sales.%20Four%20came%20from%20Poshmark%2C%20while%20one%20came%20from%20Mercari.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20better%20or%20for%20worse%2C%20I%20had%20no%20real%20sense%20of%20urgency.%20It%20allowed%20me%20to%20price%20items%20comfortably%20rather%20than%20racing%20to%20the%20bottom%20(I%20did%20end%20up%20lowering%20prices%20on%20some%20of%20my%20items)%2C%20but%20it%20also%20meant%20sales%20trickled%20in%20slowly%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20the%20project%20to%20fall%20by%20the%20wayside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20accounts%20are%20still%20active%2C%20and%20I%20even%20have%20a%20few%20listings%20live.%20If%20something%20sells%2C%20great.%20But%20I'm%20not%20planning%20to%20add%20more%20inventory%2C%20and%20I%20certainly%20won't%20be%20sourcing%20items%20beyond%20my%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReselling%20isn't%20the%20side%20hustle%20for%20me.%20It%20doesn't%20play%20to%20my%20strengths%2C%20it%20tested%20my%20patience%20at%20times%2C%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20selling%20clothes%20doesn't%20excite%20me%20enough%20to%20justify%20the%20time.%20Unlike%20the%20pickleball%20business%2C%20which%20I%20genuinely%20enjoy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lanch-ecommerce-company-startup-costs-expenses-business-budget-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edespite%20the%20stress%20and%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reselling%20felt%20like%20busywork%20that%20I%20wasn't%20even%20very%20good%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20math%20also%20only%20works%20at%20scale.%20Making%20meaningful%20money%20reselling%20clothes%20requires%20volume.%20It%20means%20constantly%20sourcing%20inventory%2C%20photographing%20items%2C%20managing%20listings%2C%20and%20shipping%20orders.%20That's%20a%20commitment%20I%20wasn't%20willing%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20who%20love%20fashion%2C%20thrifting%2C%20and%20the%20thrill%20of%20finding%20a%20deal%2C%20reselling%20can%20absolutely%20be%20lucrative%2C%20as%20I've%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now%2C%20I'm%20staying%20in%20my%20racket-sports%20lane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhustle-culture-what-its-really-like-reselling-clothing-for-profit-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769682601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697a1575e1ba468a96aad6e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhustle-culture-what-its-really-like-reselling-clothing-for-profit-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20keep%20a%20relatively%20minimal%20closet%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20handful%20of%20items%20I%20no%20longer%20wear.%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20reselling.%20How%20hard%20could%20it%20be%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhustle-cultu