and%20don't%20forget%20fiber%20and%20other%20healthy%20habits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proteinmaxxing%20trend%20has%20gone%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoading%20up%20on%20mountains%20of%20shakes%2C%20beef%20sticks%2C%20and%20chicken%20breasts%20could%20be%20making%20it%20harder%20to%20burn%20fat%2C%20according%20to%20a%20doctor%20who%20specializes%20in%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProtein%20is%20an%20essential%20nutrient%20(alongside%20carbohydrates%20and%20fats)%2C%20and%20it's%20crucial%20for%20regulating%20metabolism%2C%20as%20well%20as%20building%20and%20repairing%20tissue%20like%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotein-mistakes-health-issues-hit-your-goals-without-wasting-money-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etoo%20much%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20a%20diet%20fad%20that%20can%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20lose%20weight%20and%20distracts%20from%20nutrient-dense%20whole%20foods%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Meghan%20Garcia-Webb%2C%20who%20works%20in%20concierge%20medicine.%20Her%20practice%20is%20dedicated%20to%20helping%20high-achievers%20like%20CEOs%20and%20attorneys%20manage%20their%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20protein%20craze%20is%20totally%20out%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%20Garcia-Webb%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20want%20people%20to%20have%20protein%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20protein%20really%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientist-studies-ultra-processed-foods-rules-to-stop-overeating-simple-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eultra-processed%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20industry%20is%20making%20bank%20on%20our%20hunger%20for%20protein%20by%20adding%20it%20to%20chips%2C%20pastries%2C%20and%20bars%2C%20but%20these%20products%20don't%20offer%20much%20in%20the%20way%20of%20real%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20many%20people%20are%20getting%20more%20protein%20than%20they%20need%20because%20of%20a%20common%20mistake%20in%20calculating%20the%20optimal%20amount%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20protein%20overload%20can%20lead%20to%20excess%20calories%20that%20make%20weight%20loss%20more%20difficult%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20basic%20guidelines%20can%20help%20you%20understand%20your%20unique%20protein%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285b41ddc-ad5c-4265-921c-83a017c13789%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20eat%20enough%20protein%20for%20weight%20loss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20simple%20equation%20can%20help%20you%20understand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-protein-guidelines-how-to-eat-more-without-too-much-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20aim%20for%20each%20day%2C%20based%20on%20your%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarcia-Webb%20said%20that%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20a%20good%20range%20for%20daily%20protein%20intake%20is%20between%201%20to%201.5%20grams%20of%20protein%20per%20kilogram%20of%20your%20lean%20body%20weight%20per%20day%2C%20or%20about%200.5%20to%200.7%20grams%20per%20pound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224105%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20chunk%20of%20steak%20on%20a%20digital%20scale%20at%20a%20grocery%20store%20meat%20market%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697917e5a645d1188188149d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20may%20not%20need%20as%20much%20protein%20as%20you%20think.%3Cp%3Erbkomar%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20if%20you're%20overweight%20and%20trying%20to%20shed%20pounds%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20assess%20your%20protein%20intake%20based%20on%20your%20goal%20weight%2C%20not%20your%20current%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20consider%20a%20200-pound%20person%20trying%20to%20reach%20a%20goal%20weight%20of%20150%20pounds.%20Per%20Garcia-Webb's%20recommendation%2C%20their%20protein%20goal%20would%20be%2090%20grams%20of%20protein%20per%20day%20(in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20range%20for%20their%20goal%20weight).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20running%20the%20equation%20with%20their%20current%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20mistake%20%E2%80%94%20doesn't%20account%20for%20added%20body%20fat%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20goal%20of%20120%20grams%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20additional%20protein%20amounts%20to%20more%20than%20100%20extra%20calories.%20That%20may%20not%20sound%20like%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20it%20adds%20up%2C%20crowding%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F31-year-old-burned-body-fat-eating-more-carbs-workouts-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20energizing%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20key%20nutrients%20like%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20feel%20like%20they%20need%20to%20get%20all%20that%20protein%20or%20something%20terrible%20is%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20focusing%20on%20that%20one%20'magic'%20ingredient.%20Where%20are%20the%20vegetables%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a89e0d94-48a4-4c6d-a706-a055b8c5b211%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMake%20healthy%20eating%20sustainable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20set%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-protein-maximize-muscle-gains-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein%20goal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20more%20accurate%20and%20reasonable%20can%20help%20you%20balance%20your%20diet%2C%20Garcia-Webb%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she'd%20rather%20you%20didn't%20get%20hung%20up%20on%20a%20single%20number%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20relying%20on%20these%20external%20metrics%20of%20'I%20should%20have%20X%20many%20grams%20of%20protein'%20as%20opposed%20to%20'actually%20I%20had%20half%20of%20that%2C%20and%20I%20was%20full%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26qu