0which%20future%20capabilities%20might%20fundamentally%20change%20or%20even%20break%20their%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20takeaways%20from%20our%20Leonis%20AI%20100%20%E2%80%94%20where%20we%20benchmarked%20the%20most%20important%20AI%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20the%20strongest%20AI%20founders%20build%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20technical%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20good%20answer%20talks%20about%20entirely%20new%20workflows%20that%20get%20unlocked%2C%20not%20just%20marginal%20efficiency%20gains%2C%20and%20clearly%20explains%20how%20the%20company%20would%20adapt%20or%20pivot%20as%20the%20technology%20evolves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227be816c7-ee8b-45a5-9f5b-700992c84bfc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20what%20you're%20building%20already%20on%20the%20road%20map%20of%20a%20foundation%20model%20lab%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20AI%20startups%20don't%20fail%20because%20they're%20bad%2C%20but%20because%20they're%20building%20something%20that%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20or%20Google%20can%20eventually%20ship%20%26quot%3Bfor%20free%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20we%20don't%20accept%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20not%20focused%20on%20this%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20answer.%20We%20push%20founders%20to%20explain%20what%20internal%20constraint%20would%20actually%20prevent%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-ai-powered-consulting-startups-aily-promptql-profound-dialogue-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efoundation%20model%20lab%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20building%20the%20same%20thing.%20If%20the%20answer%20comes%20down%20to%20focus%20or%20culture%2C%20that's%20not%20a%20real%20moat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrong%20answers%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20big%20labs%20technically%20could%20build%20it%2C%20but%20doing%20so%20would%20break%20their%20incentive%20structure%2C%20pricing%2C%20or%20distribution%20model%3B%20require%20operational%20complexity%20that%20doesn't%20sc